Date of Birth: October 31, 1875<br/>
Birthplace: Henderson Creek, Idaho, USA<br/>
Ordained apostle:April 8, 1937<br/>
Death:July 15, 1953<br/>
<br/>
Born Oct. 31, 1875, at Henderson Creek, Oneida Co., Idaho, to David Bowen and Annie Schackelton. Ordained apostle April 8, 1937, by Heber J. Grant, at age 61; died July 15, 1953, at Salt Lake City, Salt Lake Co., Utah, at age 77.